snippet.title: The Slenderman Takings - Multiplayer Horror Game
snippet.description:
New multiplayer, horror game! 📣
The Slenderman Takings already available on #Steam: 
✅ https://store.steampowered.com/app/2097440/Horror_Night_The_Slenderman_takings

🏕️ Find your way out of the #forest by solving multiple puzzles, working with your team and helping other survivors, while hiding from the most famous #creepypasta: #TheSlenderman 🕴🏻

#slenderman  #HorrorGames #multiplayergames  #pvp  #pvpgames  #horrorgaming  #multiplayergames  #Horror #survival  #escapegames  #freetoplay  #fyp
